INSERT INTO `index_article` VALUES (2,'Trainable Greedy Decoding for Neural Machine Translation','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">如果看过我的这篇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">post</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/24879932\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">用</span></span>Reinforcement\nLearning<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">来做</span></span>image captioning - <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">知乎专栏</span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">）的话，应该知道用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">rl</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">做</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">seq\npredcition</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，是假设模型根据每个时刻</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">softmax</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的输出概率来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">单词的，只有满足这个假设，才能使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">reinforce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">算法。而实际上在生成过程中，大家是从来不用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的，而是用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">greedy decoding</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，或者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">beam search</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（至少在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nmt</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">image captioning</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">中是这样的）。根据我自己的实验的话，你用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">cross entropy</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">训练一个模型，如果你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，结果一般很差很差，如果用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">greedy decoding </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CIDER</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的话，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的结果大概只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">这样。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">qualitatively</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的话，也可以发现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的结果是会有错误的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>而如果你用<span lang=\"EN-US\">reinforce</span>来进行训练，你实际的训练目标不是使得你<span lang=\"EN-US\">greedy\ndecoding</span>结果更好，而是使得你<span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span>出来的结果更好。如果你跑我写的<span lang=\"EN-US\">self-critical</span>（<span lang=\"EN-US\">reinforce</span>的一种变体）的代码，就会发现，用<span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">greedy decoding</span>或者<span lang=\"EN-US\">beam search</span>几乎没有区别。我的理解是<span lang=\"EN-US\">reinforce</span>完全不<span lang=\"EN-US\">care diversity</span>，非常<span lang=\"EN-US\">mode seeking</span>，目的只是想得到一个能得高<span lang=\"EN-US\">CIDER</span>分数的<span lang=\"EN-US\">mode</span>（你会发现<span lang=\"EN-US\">reinforce</span>是会毁掉<span lang=\"EN-US\">perplexity</span>的）。（实际上我没有实际证据说最后得到的<span lang=\"EN-US\">distribution</span>是<span lang=\"EN-US\">mode seeking</span>的，因为我只看到了一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">mode</span>，可能可以用<span lang=\"EN-US\">diverse beam search</span>的算法，来看是否存在其他<span lang=\"EN-US\">mode</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>所以为了<span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span>好，模型牺牲了<span lang=\"EN-US\">diversity</span>，成就了高<span lang=\"EN-US\">cider</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>其次另外一点其实就是<span lang=\"EN-US\">training test discrepency</span>，因为<span lang=\"EN-US\">train</span>的时候是用<span lang=\"EN-US\">sample</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">test</span>的时候还是<span lang=\"EN-US\">greedy decoding</span>（或者<span lang=\"EN-US\">beam search</span>）。虽然最后<span lang=\"EN-US\">test</span>的时候也能获得高分，但实际上只能说是顺便。所以最好的就是能不能直接优化<span lang=\"EN-US\">greedy\ndecoding</span>？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n</xml><![endif]-->\n\n\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <w:WordDocument>\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>ZH-CN</w:LidThemeAsian>\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\n  <w:Compatibility>\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\n   <w:WrapTex